  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Bulwer\" title=\"House Bulwer\"><img alt=\"House Bulwer.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/8d/House_Bulwer.svg/50px-House_Bulwer.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/8d/House_Bulwer.svg/75px-House_Bulwer.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/8d/House_Bulwer.svg/100px-House_Bulwer.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Lord</span><br />Jon Bulwer</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Bulwer\" title=\"House Bulwer\"><img alt=\"House Bulwer.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/8d/House_Bulwer.svg/50px-House_Bulwer.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/8d/House_Bulwer.svg/75px-House_Bulwer.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/8d/House_Bulwer.svg/100px-House_Bulwer.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Bulwers.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Bulwers.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/bd/Bulwers.jpg/350px-Bulwers.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"223\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/bd/Bulwers.jpg/525px-Bulwers.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/bd/Bulwers.jpg/700px-Bulwers.jpg 2x\" /></a><div><a href=\"/index.php/Victaria_Tyrell\" title=\"Victaria Tyrell\">Victaria</a> and Jon Bulwer<br />Art by Paolo Puggioni</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Blackcrown\" title=\"Lord of Blackcrown\">Lord of Blackcrown</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Bulwer\" title=\"House Bulwer\">House Bulwer</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\nor before <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_279_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">279&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-ages_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-ages-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/290_AC\" title=\"290 AC\">290</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/299_AC\" title=\"299 AC\">299&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-ages_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-ages-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\nLady <a href=\"/index.php/Victaria_Tyrell\" title=\"Victaria Tyrell\">Victaria Tyrell</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Alysanne_Bulwer\" title=\"Alysanne Bulwer\">Alysanne Bulwer</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lady_Bulwer%27s_brother\" title=\"Lady Bulwer&#39;s brother\">Son</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> (possibly)</li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (appendix)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Jon Bulwer</b> was the Lord of <a href=\"/index.php/Blackcrown\" title=\"Blackcrown\">Blackcrown</a> and the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Bulwer\" title=\"House Bulwer\">House Bulwer</a> during the early reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_I_Baratheon\" title=\"Robert I Baratheon\">Robert I Baratheon</a>. He married <a href=\"/index.php/Victaria_Tyrell\" title=\"Victaria Tyrell\">Victaria Tyrell</a> and had one child with her, <a href=\"/index.php/Alysanne_Bulwer\" title=\"Alysanne Bulwer\">Alysanne</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jon_Bulwer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Jon died of a summer fever.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> His daughter <a href=\"/index.php/Alysanne_Bulwer\" title=\"Alysanne Bulwer\">Alysanne</a> succeeded him as Lady of Blackcrown and head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Bulwer\" title=\"House Bulwer\">House Bulwer</a>.\n</p><p>Jon may have a <a href=\"/index.php/Lady_Bulwer%27s_brother\" title=\"Lady Bulwer&#39;s brother\">son</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jon_Bulwer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jon</a></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Victaria_Tyrell\" title=\"Victaria Tyrell\">Victaria<br />Tyrell</a></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Jack_Bulwer\" title=\"Jack Bulwer\">Jack</a></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td></tr><tr align=\"center\"><td style=\"border-right:1px solid black\">